 International airport. At the new Integrated Passenger Terminal of Kolkata's international airport, Voltas is undertaking HVAC, internal electrification, and plumbing & drainage system works, to be completed in 24 months.</p><h6 class="card-overtitle">September 2010, Mumbai</h6><a href="https://devvoltas.voltasworld.com/images/publications/07-09-2010Voltas_secures_orders_worth_Rs_300_crores_for_airport_electro-mechanical_works.pdf_.pdf" class="press-download"><i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i> <span class="">download pdf</span></a></div></div></div>      <div class="col-12 all new-venture"><div class="card voltas-card voltas-card-press_release"><div class="card-body"><h4 class="card-title"><a href="https://devvoltas.voltasworld.com/images/publications/18-08-2010Voltas_enters_into_strategic_international_textile_technology_tie-ups.pdf_.pdf" target="_blank">Voltas enters into strategic international textile technology tie-ups</a></h4><p class="card-text">With a view to leveraging emerging opportunities in the technical textiles industry, Voltas has commenced tying-up with machinery manufacturers (principally from Europe) who are regarded as the best in their fields, with the ability to fulfil European quality norms while remaining cost-effective. These include Dilo Group, for non-woven products, Brueckner, for coating and finishing of textiles, Hansa Mixers, for coating or finishing material preparation and Wumag Texrolls, for heat setting and surface finishing of technical textiles.</p><h6 class="card-overtitle">August 2010, Mumbai</h6><a href="https://devvoltas.voltasworld.com/images/publications/18-08-2010Voltas_enters_into_strategic_international_textile_technology_tie-ups.pdf_.pdf" class="press-download"><i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i> <span class="">download pdf</span></a></div></div></div>      <div class="col-12 all new-launch"><div class="card voltas-card voltas-card-press_release"><div class="card-body"><h4 class="card-title